choices.text:
### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds
### Assistant:

Sure! Here is a sample meal plan that meets your dietary restrictions:
Breakfast: Overnight oats with almond milk, chia seeds, and mixed berries
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with spinach, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and avocado dressing
Snack: Apple slices with peanut butter
Dinner: Baked salmon with steamed broccoli and quinoa
Remember to drink plenty of water throughout the day! Let me know if you need any further assistance.
